create a new component
ng g c COMPONENTNAME

https://angular.io/cli/generate

ng g service answer<name> [options]

@Injectable({
  providedIn: 'root'
})
export class AnswerService {
providedIn 'root' tells this service can be accessed from anywhere in the application that is root of the application.
If we want to change the visibility of this service, we need to add this in the respective module file.
Here in our case this is app.module.js file

change done


